comments.body:
@ypu I'm okay with doing this is go, but seems like lots and lots of work.  This PR is almost ready for merge, along with unit-tests.  What if I add comment marking this as temporary, until your PR is ready, then we can switch meaning of 'make system-test'?

I am concerned about getting very basic system-test running early.  There are many things to do on automation-side, so having basic test now, lets that work start.  Automation work can happen in parallel, while you finish your PR.  Then I will not feel bad about throw away python tests.

Does that sound okay?
